    <p>As current practice, some Ryerson employees are eligible for University-purchased cell phone devices as determined by their leader. In these instances, the devices are University property and should be on the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/financial-services/purchasing-payment/vendors-record-common-purchases/ryerson-cell-phone-plan-with-rogers/">Ryerson cell phone plan</a>.</p> 
<p>As current practice, some Ryerson employees are required by the University to be on call and/or connected to the University at times outside the normal business hours. These employees are able to use their own device.</p>
    





